aba^{-1} = a^i b^j
a^{-1} ba = a^k b^{\ell}
i, j, k, \ell
b = a^{i + jk} b^{j \ell} = a^{k + i \ell} b^{j \ell}
j \ell = 1, i + jk = k + i \ell = 0
aba^{-1} = a^i b \Leftrightarrow b = a^{i-1} ba \Leftrightarrow bab^{-1} = a^{1-i}.
b^{-1} ab = a^m b^n
m, n
a = a^{(1-i)m} b^{(1-i)n} = a^{(1-i)m} b^n
n = 0, 1-i = m = \pm 1
